        <!-- Q8 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    求过点  <m> M_{0}(1,1,1) </m>  且与平面  <m> \Pi_{1}: x-2 y+3 z=1 </m>  及  <m> \Pi_{2}: x+y-z=2 </m>  均垂直的平面  <m> \Pi </m>  的方程. 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解  <m> \because \Pi \perp \Pi_{1} </m>  且  <m> \Pi \perp \Pi_{2} </m> ,  <m> \therefore \boldsymbol{n} \perp \boldsymbol{n}_{1} </m>  且  <m> \boldsymbol{n} \perp \boldsymbol{n}_{2} </m> , 于是
                    <me> 
                    \boldsymbol{n} / / \boldsymbol{n}_{1} \times \boldsymbol{n}_{2}=\left|\begin{array}{ccc}
                    \boldsymbol{i}  &amp;  \boldsymbol{j}  &amp;  \boldsymbol{k} \\
                    1  &amp;  -2  &amp;  3 \\
                    1  &amp;  1  &amp;  -1
                    \end{array}\right|=-\boldsymbol{i}+4 \boldsymbol{j}+3 \boldsymbol{k},
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 可取  <m> \boldsymbol{n}=(1,-4,-3) </m> . 又因为  <m> \Pi </m>  过  <m> M_{0} </m>  点, 故由点法式知
                    <me> 
                    \Pi:(x-1)-4(y-1)-3(z-1)=0,
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 即  <m> \Pi: x-4 y-3 z+6=0 </m> . 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q9 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    求过点  <m> M_{1}(1,1,8), M_{2}(2,-5,0) </m>  和  <m> M_{3}(4,7,1) </m>  的平面  <m> \Pi </m>  的方程. </p> 

                <p> 若已知  <m> \Pi </m>  上不共线的三个点  <m> M_{1}, M_{2}, M_{3} </m> ,则可按下面的方法求得其点法式方程: </p> 

                <p> (1)作向量  <m> \overrightarrow{M_{1} M_{2}}, \overrightarrow{M_{1} M_{3}} \subset \Pi </m> ;
                (2)取  <m> \boldsymbol{n} / / \overrightarrow{M_{1} M_{2}} \times \overrightarrow{M_{1} M_{3}} </m> ;
                (3) 由  <m> \boldsymbol{n} </m>  及  <m> M_{1} </m>  (或  <m> M_{2} </m> , 或  <m> M_{3} </m>  )写出  <m> \Pi </m>  的点法式方程. 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解 (1)作  <m> \overrightarrow{M_{1} M_{2}}=(1,-6,-8) </m> ,  <m> \overrightarrow{M_{1} M_{3}}=(3,6,-7). </m>  </p> 

                    <p> (2)  <m> \overrightarrow{M_{1} M_{2}} \times \overrightarrow{M_{1} M_{3}}=\left|\begin{array}{ccc}\boldsymbol{i}  &amp;  \boldsymbol{j}  &amp;  \boldsymbol{k} \\ 1  &amp;  -6  &amp;  -8 \\ 3  &amp;  6  &amp;  -7\end{array}\right|=(90,-17,24) </m> ,
                    取  <m>  \boldsymbol{n}=(90,-17,24)  </m> . </p> 

                    <p> (3)  <m> \Pi: 90(x-1)-17(y-1)+24(z-8)=0  </m> , </p> 

