        <!-- Q10 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设  <m> L:\left\{\begin{array}{l}x+y+z+1=0, \\ 2 x+3 y-z+4=0,\end{array}\right. </m>  求  <m> L </m>  的标准方程. 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解 (1)求  <m> L </m>  上的一点  <m> M_{0}\left(x_{0}, y_{0}, z_{0}\right) </m>  :
                    若设  <m> x_{0}=1 </m> , 则由  <m> \left\{\begin{array}{l}y_{0}+z_{0}=-2, \\ 3 y_{0}-z_{0}=-6\end{array}\right. </m>  解得  <m> y_{0}=-2, z_{0}=0 </m> , </p> 

                    <p> (2)求  <m> L </m>  的一个方向向量  <m> s </m>  :
                    因为面交式方程中的两个平面的法向量分别为  <m> \boldsymbol{n}_{1}=(1,1,1), \boldsymbol{n}_{2}=(2,3,-1) </m> , 而  <m> \boldsymbol{s} \perp \boldsymbol{n}_{1} </m>  且  <m> \boldsymbol{s} \perp \boldsymbol{n}_{2} </m> , 故可取
                    <me> 
                    \boldsymbol{s}=\boldsymbol{n}_{1} \times \boldsymbol{n}_{2}=\left|\begin{array}{ccc}
                    \boldsymbol{i}  &amp;  \boldsymbol{j}  &amp;  \boldsymbol{k} \\
                    1  &amp;  1  &amp;  1 \\
                    2  &amp;  3  &amp;  -1
                    \end{array}\right|=-4 \boldsymbol{i}+3 \boldsymbol{j}+\boldsymbol{k} .
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> (3)写出  <m> L </m>  的点向式方程:  <m> \frac{x-1}{-4}=\frac{y+2}{3}=\frac{z}{1} </m> . 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

